The paper deals with deep learning-based iris recognition using visible spectrum and NIR images. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, since the paper focuses on iris recognition, it may also belong to the image and video processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, since the paper deals with security and biometrics, it may also belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
